director.name: 希维亚·艾巴斯卡 Silvia Abascal

introduction: A lonely house in the countryside. Inside, an absent woman, completely wrapped in her nighttime trance. We don't know where her emptiness comes from or whats wrong with her. Only an unexpected noise outside manages to wake her from her idleness. A man has jumped over the fence and entered her yard. She tries to stop him from breaking in but its too late. the stranger make it inside living room. Two strangers, face to face. He wants everything, she has nothing left.
